messages.TRMSG_PRE_BATTLE:
To find my favorite Pokémon, I’ll go
east, west, or any which way!
messages.TRMSG_POST_BATTLE:
If you’re trying to find the Pokémon
you want, you need to go everywhere!Not just east and west, either.
South and north are important, too!
messages.TRMSG_REMATCH:
For my favorite Pokémon, I’ll go
east, west, or any which way!...Saying that, I’ve been wandering
around here all this time.
